Well...

1066
01:03:02,786 --> 01:03:04,853
uh, one of the lights
wasn't working,

1067
01:03:04,855 --> 01:03:07,490
so I thought I'd
take it back to the workshop

1068
01:03:07,492 --> 01:03:10,126
and see if I could fix it.

1069
01:03:10,128 --> 01:03:11,994
