1070
01:03:11,996 --> 01:03:13,496
Yeah. Sure.

1071
01:03:13,498 --> 01:03:16,332
Now, why don't you
go back upstairs to bed,

1072
01:03:16,334 --> 01:03:18,333
and then when you wake up,
the tree will be fixed

1073
01:03:18,335 --> 01:03:20,102
