- Wait.

1074
01:03:20,104 --> 01:03:22,004
You don't understand.
I don't want presents.

1075
01:03:22,006 --> 01:03:24,840
Of course you do.
Everyone wants presents.

1076
01:03:24,842 --> 01:03:28,377
