for other people.

1080
01:03:36,187 --> 01:03:39,288
And I just want her
to be happy.

1081
01:03:39,290 --> 01:03:41,989
You want me to help...
your mom?

1082
01:03:41,991 --> 01:03:43,991
You're Santa.

1083
01:03:43,993 --> 01:03:45,993
You make people happy.

1084
01:03:45,995 --> 01:03:50,064
