should be happy, right?

1085
01:03:50,066 --> 01:03:52,333
Y-Yeah, I...

1086
01:03:52,335 --> 01:03:55,102
I guess they should.

1087
01:03:55,104 --> 01:03:56,437
Santa,

1088
01:03:56,439 --> 01:03:59,040
are... are you okay?

1089
