with us tomorrow.

1094
01:04:11,119 --> 01:04:13,421
We all get together and sing.

1095
01:04:13,423 --> 01:04:16,122
It's so beautiful that

1096
01:04:16,124 --> 01:04:19,359
if you close your eyes
and listen,

1097
01:04:19,361 --> 01:04:22,965
