just goes away.

1098
01:04:26,435 --> 01:04:29,135
That sounds nice.

1099
01:04:30,239 --> 01:04:31,438
Huh?

1100
01:04:35,977 --> 01:04:38,278
Thank you, Santa.

1101
01:04:38,280 --> 01:04:40,282
Good night.

1102
01:04:43,084 --> 01:04:45,119
Good-good night.

1103
01:04:58,266 --> 01:05:01,969
